##Loading a CSS Style Sheet on the Fly

The easiest way is to dynamically insert the style sheet on the head. This can be achieved with a small piece of jQuery code.

<pre>
<code>
var link = $("<link>");
link.attr({
        type: 'text/css',
        rel: 'stylesheet',
        href: <your CSS file url>
});
$("head").append( link ); 
</code>
</pre>

Read more at the [jQuery Forum](http://forum.jquery.com/topic/loading-stylesheets-on-the-fly)
  